    <h2>Leaktight automata</h2>

    <br/>
    <h3><b>Theorem</b></h3> The Markov Monoid algorithm is correct for <i>leaktight automata</i>

    <div class="slide_step"><center><img id="classes" src="img/history.svg"/></center></div>

