    <br/>
    <br/>
    <h3><b>Theorem</b></h3> All classes for which the value 1 problem is decidable are strictly included in the class of <i>leaktight automata</i>

    <br/>
    <br/>
    <div class="slide_step">
    <h3>Is the class of leaktight automata maximal?</h3>
    </div>
